  "detailed_description": "<h1>The game is available in Early Access</h1><p><strong>The game is available in Early Access!</strong><br>Always welcome your wishes and ideas.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Azy is a skilled demon hunter. Having learned about the infernal cult, the main character went in search of the lost hall, which connects six worlds. Now you have to destroy the inhabitants of each of these worlds.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.poster.avif?t=1713262391\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.webm?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.mp4?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Retro first person shooter.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No sections with platforming that can be annoying at times.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/11b99f40ea663599a951dbce41854267.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br><br></li><li>No petty enemies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.poster.avif?t=1713262391\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.webm?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.mp4?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Each boss has a HealthBar.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/05bd31ddc5787d73e690cb925dbb86c9.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br><br></li><li>No reloading weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/fd49ed650bfa819361ea4369b2e617bd.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br> <br></li><li>Six different themes and each theme has its own unique enemies.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Azy is a skilled demon hunter. Having learned about the infernal cult, the main character went in search of the lost hall, which connects six worlds. Now you have to destroy the inhabitants of each of these worlds.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.poster.avif?t=1713262391\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.webm?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/1ed4125d8214efbfd1db37fdd027e0d7.mp4?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Retro first person shooter.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No sections with platforming that can be annoying at times.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/11b99f40ea663599a951dbce41854267.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br><br></li><li>No petty enemies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.poster.avif?t=1713262391\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.webm?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/b56de651eb87575a2e962b25882c347e.mp4?t=1713262391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Each boss has a HealthBar.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/05bd31ddc5787d73e690cb925dbb86c9.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br><br></li><li>No reloading weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573110/extras/fd49ed650bfa819361ea4369b2e617bd.avif?t=1713262391\" width=640 height=154 /></span><br> <br></li><li>Six different themes and each theme has its own unique enemies.</li></ul>",
